1
00:00:00,950 --> 00:00:03,720
I have something I need to tell you all.

2
00:00:03,720 --> 00:00:06,200
What is it?

3
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:09,780
I plan on... selling this house.

4
00:00:09,780 --> 00:00:11,510
- What?
- What?

5
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:14,280
That puts us in a bind. What will <i>we</i> do?

6
00:00:14,280 --> 00:00:16,270
Are we back to hotel hopping?

7
00:00:16,270 --> 00:00:20,120
Mom, isn't that inconvenient for you too?

8
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:22,340
I suppose so.

9
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:25,900
Sorry, I know I said you could stay as long as you'd like,

10
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:29,340
but I've already made my decision.

11
00:00:30,520 --> 00:00:34,470
Are you getting married to Takaya?

12
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:36,830
Isn't that why you're selling this house?

13
00:00:36,830 --> 00:00:37,820
Is that true?

14
00:00:37,820 --> 00:00:42,090
No, I'm not marrying Takaya.

15
00:00:42,090 --> 00:00:43,660
Rather...

16
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:48,040
I won't marry anyone ever again.

17
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:49,710
That's extreme.

18
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,170
Then why are you selling this place?

19
00:00:52,170 --> 00:00:54,320
Because...

20
00:00:55,350 --> 00:00:59,050
<i>I've decided to date her.</i>

21
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:02,410
Because what?

22
00:01:02,410 --> 00:01:04,800
Anyhow, I'm selling this place.

23
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:07,980
Kaede, Azusa, Mom,

24
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:11,390
please think about your future plans.

25
